<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">

    <h1>About me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: "100%", alt: "Profile image" %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
               <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
               <div class="progress">
                   <div 
                      class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                      role="progressbar"
                      aria-valuenow="<%=skill.percent_utilized %>"
                      aria-valuemax="100"
                      style="width: <%=skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                    >
                    </div>
               </div>
            </div>            
          <% end %> 
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="col-md-8">
     
        <p class="lead">
           For a long time, I've been working in IT projects, fulfilling all kind of roles.
           Outside working hours I've worked on non profit voluntary projects regularly, to contribute to a more beautiful world.
           However, this has not always been very effective. And as a result of that was sometimes even quite frustrating!
           Due to the Corono crisis I have decided to dedicate a part of my workweek to a non profit project.
           In this project I'm going to create a platform that joins people and projects that contribute to a more beautiful world. 
           The platform will help creating a network, a community of people working on all kinds op initiatives and projects, helping each other.
        </p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"  
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            area-expanded="false"
            area-controller="jobHistory"

          >
            Job History
          </button>
           <button
            class="btn btn-primary"  
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            area-expanded="false"
            area-controller="education"

          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Application Engineer
            </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
              Test Manager
            </div>
          </div>

            <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              HIO
            </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
              Koninklijke Luchtmacht
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Landbouw Universiteit Wageningen
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


